naengmyeon
beef brisket
mu radish
carrot
1 Pear
cucumber
egg
sesame seeds
4Tbsp Sesame oil
1/2 Onion
1C Gochugaru
5tbsp Gochujang
1Tbsp Sugar
1Tbsp soy sauce
4tbsp white vinegar
4 cloves garlic







MISE


Show Naengmyeon
Show Gochugaru
Show Gochujang
Peel Garlic
Chop Pear
Chop Onion
Julienne Radish
Julienne Carrot
Julienne Cucumber


COOK

Boil beef in water 1hr
Skim
Cool
Freeze

Boil egg
Peel
Slice

Radish in bowl
Add sugar
water
vinegar
Refrigerate

Puree in blender:
	onion
	garlic
	pear
	sugar
	salt


Pour into bowl
Add:
	gochugaru
	gochujang
	soy sauce
	vinegar
	sesame oil

Refrigerate

Next Day

Boil noodles
chill in ice water